{"tid":1584383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【港人講地】【暴力打殘經濟】暴力示威不斷 會展業生意受衝擊","createTime":"2019-09-21T05:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T05:49:54.000Z","uid":325258,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5dd2f91b960fb9279ab44090d500c77797f1e5e","tid":1584383,"uid":325258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:45:11.000Z","msg":"【港人講地】反修例風波持續，暴力示威衝擊不斷。香港不穩定的局面令會展業亦受影響。貿發局表示，近月個別展覽活動入場人數下跌，但影響尚未算嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n近日已有三十多年歷史的珠寶首飾展在灣仔會展舉行，有出席的內地參展商就表示，生意比去年少近三成，主要缺少了美國客人。有珠寶展參展商表示，因應香港出現的暴力示威，有些國家將香港列入旅遊警示名單，買家前來參與展覽的意欲減低。<br />\n<br />\n香港展覽會議業協會會長李劍彬在接受傳媒訪問時指出，最主要的買家雖然仍有來港，但與過往不同的是，現時買家單獨前來，並非與採購團隊一起。他透露有海外人士從新聞上看到示威，當中示威者對警察的暴力行為令他們十分擔憂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBYXjhU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBYXjhU.jpg&h=213b01c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/48852/-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E6%89%93%E6%AE%98%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7-%E6%9C%83%E5%B1%95%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E5%8F%97%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%25E7%2584%25A6%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F48852%2F-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25AE%2598%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2596%25B7-%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25A1%259D%25E6%2593%258A&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd7xPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=4d249865\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/%E7%84%A6%E9%BB%9E%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/48852/-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E6%89%93%E6%AE%98%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7-%E6%9C%83%E5%B1%95%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E5%8F%97%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A</a>"},{"pid":"42685c55b53661140db21a1b9e99c50fa147721b","tid":1584383,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:46:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"c05d878e8371ca98279c39591c4b530d77b104d2","tid":1584383,"uid":3324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"樓主相當有可疑"},{"pid":"43ecc08913645a84dfdf04e4cd0a4ebf86ee1739","tid":1584383,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:47:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"86b742e74706e9c77bc1591be716df1d807f913f","tid":1584383,"uid":31549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"本身成行生意都差左幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇反送中遲早都要執一堆跟唔上時代既公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}